            "body": "<blockquote>\n  <p>I have a keyListener on the JTextField that commits data to the model when the \"enter\" key is pushed. <\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>Probably not related to your problem, but you should be using an ActionListener to handle the Enter key, not a KeyListener.<\/p>\n",
